name: Backdraft
description: Joran makes a final power play and decides to make use of his host - by forcing his way into the Celestial Temple! What will Joran do there? What will happen to the wormhole? It will take Starfleet's best and brightest to protect this vital point.
rules:
-- Unique Dominion, Bajoran and Cardassian Faction Missions are available during the event. Open the Event to access them.
-- Using Joran Sisko, any version of O'Brien, Dax, or Trill crew will provide a bonus to Event Faction Missions.
-- Every Event Faction Mission you succeed at earns you Event Victory Points. Collect Victory Points to unlock Event Threshold Rewards.
-- In this event, Squadrons may also compete to advance up the Squadron leaderboards. Join a Squadron to get more rewards!
bonus_text: Crew Bonus: Joran Sisko, O'Brien, Dax, or Trill crew
rewards_teaser: Reach Rank 1 by gaining Victory Points from Event Missions!

featured_crew.name: Scotty
